OL,3,CClimate commission critical to
OL,4,Censuring 'fair, inclusive transition',
OL,5,Csays Muir
OL,7,FThe Stormont Agriculture Minister
OL,8,FAndrew Muir is to bring forward
OL,9,Fregulations to establish a Just
OL,10,FTransition Commission to help steer
OL,11,Fclimate-change policy in Northern
OL,12,FIreland.
OL,14,FJust Transition Commissions already
OL,15,Foperate in Scotland and the Republic
OL,16,Fof Ireland, where they provide advice
OL,17,Fand scrutiny to governments as they
OL,18,Fwork towards low-carbon targets.
