OL,3,CClimate commission critical to
OL,4,Censuring 'fair, inclusive transition',
OL,5,Csays Muir
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's proposed commission
OL,8,Fwill include representatives from a
OL,9,Frange of sectors, including
OL,10,Fagriculture, environmental groups,
OL,11,Ftrade unions and youth organisations.
OL,13,FMr Muir confirmed he will bring draft
OL,14,Fregulations to the Department of
OL,15,FAgriculture, Environment and Rural
OL,16,FAffairs (DAERA) committee and the
OL,17,FAssembly for scrutiny.
