OL,3,CClimate commission critical to
OL,4,Censuring 'fair, inclusive transition',
OL,5,Csays Muir
OL,7,FHe described the move as "a critical
OL,8,Fstep" in ensuring Northern Ireland has
OL,9,Fthe right structures in place to
OL,10,Faddress the challenges and
OL,11,Fopportunities linked to climate action.
OL,13,F"At all times, we must ensure that
OL,14,Fthis is done in a way that is
OL,15,Finclusive, fair and sustainable," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
