OL,3,CClimate commission critical to
OL,4,Censuring 'fair, inclusive transition',
OL,5,Csays Muir
OL,7,F"The establishment of a Just
OL,8,FTransition Commission will be
OL,9,Fessential to delivering on this
OL,10,Fambition. Through its oversight and
OL,11,Fadvisory role, it will help ensure
OL,12,Fthat government departments design
OL,13,Fdecarbonisation policies that ensure
OL,14,Fnobody is left behind.
OL,16,FThe draft regulations follow a 10-week
OL,17,Fpublic consultation, which showed
OL,18,Fstrong support for the creation of a
OL,19,Fcommission to help Executive
OL,20,Fdepartments ensure climate policies
OL,21,Fwork for everyone in Northern Ireland.
