OL,3,CClimate commission critical to
OL,4,Censuring 'fair, inclusive transition',
OL,5,Csays Muir
OL,7,FMr Muir said progress on the
OL,8,Fcommission marked "an important
OL,9,Fmilestone" and that he looked forward
OL,10,Fto further discussion during the
OL,11,FAssembly scrutiny process.
OL,13,FThe commission's main role will be to
OL,14,Foversee how departments implement the
OL,15,Ftransition to lower emissions and to
OL,16,Fadvise on whether climate policies
OL,17,Fcomply with the principles and
OL,18,Fobjectives of a just transition set
OL,19,Fout in legislation.
